name: Cassini Cuisini
description:
Deliver food to hungry customers in space. Most aspects are very unfinished.

Mouse: Pitch/Yaw

W/S: Accellerate and decellerate

A/D: Strafe

Space/Ctrl: Up and down

Q/E: Roll

Shift: Boost

Mouse 1: Deliver food

Mouse scroll: Select food

Made by turbosocks and treeboater for 7dfps 2020
